     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <l>
      <seg rend="decorInit">W</seg>Hē reader thou doest read this booke,</l>
   <l>With frownyng forhed doe not looke:</l>
   <l>For <hi>Cato</hi> curste, nor <hi>Curius,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>Nor frownyng sowre <hi>Heraclitus,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>These are not made: but if thei bende</l>
   <l>Their eyes to see what here is pende:</l>
   <l>Suche toyes thei shall bee sure to finde</l>
   <l>As will refreshe the mestfull minde.</l>
</div>
